OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with some light rain,
OL,6,Fmainly for western areas but generally
OL,7,Fdrier and brighter around the Moray
OL,8,FFirth. A few afternoon showers
OL,9,Fdeveloping in the light westerly
OL,10,Fbreeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRather cloudy with a few
OL,13,Fshowery outbreaks of rain in the
OL,14,Fevening. Through the rest of the night
OL,15,Fcloudy conditions will continue with
OL,16,Ffurther showers at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
