OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FMainly cloudy in the morning
OL,6,Fwith showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,7,FTurning brighter but with a risk of
OL,8,Ffurther showers for a time in the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,12,Fand settled conditions prevail through
OL,13,Fthis period with light winds. Patchy
OL,14,Fcloud develops on Tuesday, before
OL,15,Fplenty of sunshine is expected on
OL,16,FWednesday and Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
